MSA_WITH_TARGET_MAKRETS %>% 
  filter(TARGET_MARKET==0) %>% 
  left_join(distance_scores, by = 'GEOID') %>% 
  select(-Distance_Bucket, -GEOID, -TARGET_MARKET) %>% 
  lm(Total_Dist~., data = .) %>% 
  summary() %>% 
  print() %>% 
  broom::tidy() %>% 
  filter(p.value<0.05) %>% 
  arrange(estimate)
